org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel

Class HSSFShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shape
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HSSFShapeGroup, HSSFSimpleShape 

    public abstract class HSSFShape
extends java.lang.Object
implements Shape
    An abstract shape. Note: Microsoft Excel seems to sometimes disallow higher y1 than y2 or higher x1 than x2 in the anchor, you might need to reverse them and draw shapes vertically or horizontally flipped via setFlipVertical() or setFlipHorizontally().(一个抽象的形状。注：Microsoft Excel似乎有时不允许锚点中的y1高于y2或x1高于x2，您可能需要颠倒它们并通过setFlipVertical（）或setFlipHorizontally（）垂直或水平翻转绘制形状。)

      • setAnchor

        public void setAnchor(HSSFAnchor anchor)
        Sets a particular anchor. A top-level shape must have an anchor of HSSFClientAnchor. A child anchor must have an anchor of HSSFChildAnchor(设置特定的锚点。顶级形状必须具有HSSFClientAnchor的锚点。儿童锚必须拥有HSSFChildAnchor的锚)
        Parameters:
        anchor - the anchor to use.(锚-要使用的锚。)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when the wrong anchor is used for this particular shape.(java.lang. IllegalArgument例外-当错误的锚点用于此特定形状时。)
        See Also:
        HSSFChildAnchor, HSSFClientAnchor

        public int getRotationDegree()

        the rotation, in degrees, that is applied to a shape.(应用于形状的旋转（以度为单位）。)

      • setRotationDegree

        public void setRotationDegree(short value)
        specifies the rotation, in degrees, that is applied to a shape. Positive values specify rotation in the clockwise direction. Negative values specify rotation in the counterclockwise direction. Rotation occurs around the center of the shape. The default value for this property is 0x00000000(指定应用于形状的旋转（以度为单位）。正值指定顺时针方向的旋转。负值指定逆时针方向的旋转。旋转围绕形状的中心发生。此属性的默认值为0x 0000000)
        Parameters:
        value -(价值-)
